snippet.title: Episode 2 - A Bleaker Predicklement
snippet.description:
The next thrilling installment of the Adventures of Bertram Fiddle is almost ready!
Prepare yourself for more murder, mystery and puns!
Unfortunately NOT coming this November
Now scheduled for early 2017! Probably due to Brexit.

Follow my adventures on Twitter @bertramfiddle
And check out our Steam Page http://store.steampowered.com//app/489930
Huzzah!
